proc defineGlobals(globals: PGlobals; m: BModule; vars: openArray[PSym]) {.
    ...raises: [KeyError, Exception, ERecoverableError],
    tags: [ReadDirEffect, RootEffect].}
Emits definitions for the items in vars into the top-level section, with m being the module the globals belong to. Also updates each symbol that requires name mangling with the mangled name.   Source   Edit
